---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const title = "About Us";
---

<Layout title={title}>
  <main>
    <h1>{title}</h1>
    <div class="boxLeft">
      <p class="first">
        <strong>Sound in Motion</strong> (a.k.a. SiM) is a renowned shop specializing
        in sales and installations of High Performance Car Audio systems, as well
        as Video, Multimedia, Navigation, Alarms and Remote Car Starters. With over
        50 years of combined experience, Sound in Motion is one of the most recognized
        Mobile Electronics Specialty Retailers in the nation.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Established in 1988</strong> Sound in Motion is well known for its
        multi-award winning installations (see <a href="installs.html"
          >Installs</a
        > section), several of which have been featured in national and international
        magazines (see <a href="publications.html">Publications</a> section). Many
        years have been spent designing and building competition vehicles. The result
        is a showroom full of trophies including two IASCA World Championships along
        with a lot of experience we now can offer to you. Read what of all our customers
        have to say (see the <a href="testimonials.html">
          Testimonials
        </a>section).
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Sound in Motion</strong> is an authorized dealer for most of the
        high quality top name brands at competitive prices (visit our of <a
          href="products.html">Product Lines</a
        > section). All of our installations are performed with the utmost care and
        highest quality of craftsmanship by trained and experienced technicians.
        We offer a lifetime warranty on all of our work for as long as you own the
        vehicle. Please call or come visit our store (see our<a
          href="contact.html"
        >
          Contact</a
        > section), so we can consult your Mobile Electronics needs.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="boxRight">
      <div class="bio first">
        <a
